CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 13, 1971, pg. 18, reads: "Cooking Corner - Famous Lloyd Rolls - Mrs. Rose Lloyd, whose roll are famous, released the recipe especially for the The Courier readers 'Kitchen Corner.'" Rose Lee Lloyd (c.1917-2003) was a foster parent and founding member of the Allegheny County Foster Parent Guild in 1959.
TitMainTitle: Rose Lee Lloyd holding tray of rolls and standing in her kitchen
